Package: polrep
Type: Package
Title: Calculate political representation scores
Version: 0.7
Date: 2012-07-04
Author: Didier Ruedin
Maintainer: Didier Ruedin <didier.ruedin@wolfson.oxon.org>
Description: Package to calculate political representation scores. Includes a large number of (potential) measures of political representation, including individual representation scores (IRS), the Gallagher index of leas squares, Q-scores (Rose index), and R-scores (relative representation scores).
License: GPL-3
